HEADWORD: Fretten
<hw>Fret"ten</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[The old p. p. of
fret to rub.]</ety> <def>Rubbed; marked; <as>as, pock-<ex>fretten</ex>,
marked with the smallpox</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

